      "actionDate": "2025-05-19",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in Senate",
      "text": "<p><strong>Promoting Access to Diabetic Shoes Act</strong></p> <p>This bill allows a nurse practitioner or physician assistant to fulfill documentation requirements for coverage, under Medicare,&nbsp;of special shoes for diabetic individuals. Under current law, such requirements may be satisfied only by a physician.</p>",
